                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>This seems to point to some error in the census of 1853<ref target="#foot.f2"/>   The an-decrease percent from 1850 to 1860 is 2<hi rend="superscript">.</hi>01—much more in accordance with the other results. The population given for 1853 is more likely that for 1858— is the date right.<ref target="#foot.f3"/></p> 

